			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If anyone thinks an SMR is worth *more* than this robe, they are a fool.<BR>
<BR>
Prices are set on items based on their stats, and how difficult they are to obtain.  The Ishva robe has better stats than an SMR if your INT is already over 200.  Any established server has a ton of casters who have long since maxxed out their INT.<BR>
<BR>
The robe is also dropped much less frequently than an SMR.  This alone makes it worth more.  Do the math, its not that hard to figure out.  If you don't believe me, just camp it yourself.  Its possible to be lucky and kill it 1 time and get a robe, but that doesn't happen very often.<BR>
<BR>
Finally, look around on most servers.  Just about every L45+ is running around in an SMR.  There will never be near as many Ishva robes.  If you think this robe is worth only 4-5k, you are seriously mistaken.
				</font>
			</td>

